<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 21pt; caret-color: red; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">时序更迭，岁末将至。2023学年匆匆流逝已到终点，回首过往，江西软件职业技术大学经济管理学院已圆满完成了本学期的工作计划。2024年1月19日，学院召开全院教职工会议,总结过往谋篇启程，砥砺前行筑梦远航。同时,在会议的最后,学院为一月份生日的老师们举行了一次暖心的集体生日。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 21pt; caret-color: red; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">本次会议由经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平和常务副院长颜小燕主持，全院教职工参加。</span></p><p></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="138079" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; flex-direction: column;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(248, 213, 157);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-right: 1px solid rgb(248, 213, 157); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(248, 213, 157); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 242); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240126/1706235550546061564.jpg" title="1706235550546061564.jpg" alt="5cd139d2acba47792d659fa9d159c474.jpg" width="650" height="331" style="width: 650px; height: 331px;"/></p>